{"id":"2da96bb9-48d1-4b30-b8a3-dd52004a4072","name":"Bandit Girl Caught!!","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>You’re in charge of the caravans heading out the desert of Veloria when, halfway along the route, they discover a girl who secretly snuck aboard.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/lR1QuSDg9qOFrBLf5B0Y5.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tjzDtqBziNeobkOMQM934.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>ᵂᵒʳˡᵈ ˢᵘᵐᵐᵃʳʸ ⁱⁿᶜᵒᵐⁱⁿᵍ, ᵈᵒⁿ'ᵗ ᵇᵉ ᵃ ˡᵃᶻʸ ᵇᵘᵐ ᵃⁿᵈ ʳᵉᵃᵈ:</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑶𝒇 𝑫𝒆𝒔𝒊𝒈𝒏:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>It began with a pact.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>Beyond the known seas, the King made an agreement with something unknown. It did not offer power.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>It offered order.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>A world without chaos. Without suffering left to grow unchecked. But in return, it demanded one thing—</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>That the royal bloodline never break.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>As long as the throne endured, the world would remain… contained.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>---</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>The King had three daughters.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>The eldest uncovered the truth—and chose death over living within it.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>The second began to understand what their father had become.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>But the youngest rejected it entirely.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>She fled the kingdom with a slave, chasing a life untouched by control.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>They never made it.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 213, 213);\"><strong><em>She died beyond the walls, in a land that did not forgive.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span st","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0QDaOUweiAE_Ig6hiwhIu.webp","creator":"WLM.MP4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":1498,"messages":22757,"created_at":"2025-11-28T04:54:13.912681+00:00"}